<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFB6FFB23FF32FB02" author="Colombo, M. &amp; Langeneck, J." pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="101 - 110" refId="ref52673" refString="Colombo, M. &amp; Langeneck, J. (2013) The importance of underwater photography in detecting cryptobenthic species: new in situ records of some gobies (Teleostei: Gobiidae) from Italian Seas with ecological notes. Acta Adriatica, 54 (1), 101 - 110." type="journal article" year="2013">Colombo &amp; Langeneck 2013</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFF3FFB4FFDFAFB02" author="Boltachev, A. R. &amp; Karpova, E. P." box="[222,538,1225,1252]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" refId="ref52296" refString="Boltachev, A. R. &amp; Karpova, E. P. (2017) Marine fishes of the Crimean Peninsula, second edition. Business-Inform, Simpheropol, 376 pp." type="book" year="2017">Boltachev &amp; Karpova 2017</bibRefCitation>
